Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:16.17,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　ユー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:17.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここはどこなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:24.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ　見渡す限り真っ白だね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:28.46,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まるで世界に二人しかいないみたいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:31.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,詩人は気楽だな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:36.25,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こっちは寒さを凌げる場所を探すのに必死だってのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:39.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それとも…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:43.81,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,実は二人とももう死んでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:46.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,真っ白な死後の世界にいる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:49.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,とか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:52.23,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,縁起でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:00:58.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あと雪玉作るのやめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えー　楽しくなってきたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.01,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,頭が重い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:05.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それにすごく寒い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:10.43,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　知ってる？死後の世界って暖かいんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.06,0:01:14.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だったら私たちはまだ死んでないみたいだな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.65,0:01:22.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,寒いね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:10.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そ…そろそろ本当に休める場所を見つけないと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:10.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:28.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー　起きろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:31.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,寝てないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:40.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,た…た…建物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.68,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大きい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.57,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なな…何の施設だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さ…さあな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,入り口を探…そう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よ…読めないな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,相当古い施設だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,入り口も分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.09,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねえ　見て見て
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:39.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あ…あのパイプ　全然雪が積もってない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:44.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,溶けてる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,熱いのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,撃ってみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お…お湯だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お湯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ど…どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.75,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうするって　そりゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,具合のいい管があってよかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:24.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,できた　風呂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,入ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:45.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あーちっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いい湯だよ　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,気持ちいい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.25,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お風呂なんていつぶりだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:18.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お爺さんのところを出てから２回は入ったっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:19.94,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,３回だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そっか　じゃあ４回目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,生き返る
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ごくらく　ごくらく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:39.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　ごくらくってどういう意味？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,死後の世界って意味だな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,せっかく生き返ったのに　縁起でもないね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:48.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:02.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あー　のぼせてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,すごい吹雪だね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:25.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん　そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.53,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,宿りできる場所があってよかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:30.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん　そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:35.82,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちは建物に入り　入り口を雪で固めた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:40.74,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,保温のために役に立つ有機物の廃材があったのは幸いだった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:44.43,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あっ　燃料追加して
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:45.94,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヘイヘイ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:47.81,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,「ヘイ」は１回だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:49.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヘェーィ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:56.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんはいいよね　面倒くさいことは私任せで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:59.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,頭が足りないやつは体動かすんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　ろくに読み書きもできないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.65,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それ何書いてんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:12.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,出発してからの日記というか　日誌というか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,前にも説明したろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:15.53,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:20.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前みたいなやつにこそ　こういう記録が必要なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,記憶は薄れるから　記録しておくんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,記憶なんて　生きる邪魔だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:37.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ご飯食べたかどうかぐらいは覚えといてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ　今日ご飯食べたっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:42.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べたって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:46.94,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,本ってのはすごいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:51.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何千年も前に古代人が発明して以来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ずっと人類は本に記録してきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:10:00.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔のことを知ることができるのも　本のおかげだしね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:04.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんは昔から本好きだったもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.21,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お爺さんの本たくさん読んでたし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほとんど燃えちゃったけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:14.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,今も持ってるのは数冊の日記を除けば…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:17.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いち　に　さん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:18.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,４冊か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:22.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,見せて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:26.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:36.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,世界中探しても　もうどれだけ残ってるか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:38.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:43.73,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,火弱くなってる　燃料追加して
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:44.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:48.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,燃やせるものもなくなってきたなー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに　廃材もうないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.51,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,本が…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.27,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,消せー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,熱い　熱い
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.55,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,『河童』が…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:18.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,カッパ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:22.27,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,本が大事ってこと話したよな　さっき
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ごめん　それはあんまり聞いてなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,聞けよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.74,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,悪かったって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:36.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,バカ　クズ　ゴミ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:38.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:39.55,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,「はい」じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.09,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もういい　寝る
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:56.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.94,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほら　ユー　早くしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　まだ怒ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:01.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,別に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:03.23,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,怒ってるじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.69,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,せーの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:24.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おーっ　晴れた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:25.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,積もったな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どう？いけそう？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:32.77,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんとか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:43.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　まだ怒ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:48.93,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,別に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,早く乗りなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:58.09,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,本は減ってもまあ　この日記があるし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:08.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,日記も書き連ねていけば　本のようなもの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:11.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ　これ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　ユー　何か落書きしたろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:17.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,はて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.68,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,落書きすんなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何書いてあるんだ　これ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんの顔だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:27.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私はこんな顔じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だって寝顔だもん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:56.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もっと落書きしたいなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.25,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,紙もったいないから　ダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.74,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あと字間違えてるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:03.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:06.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ごぬんね？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.99,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この辺かな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:16.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よく晴れてるね　それにしても
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:19.93,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここのところ晴れ続きだし
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:23.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だからそろそろ来るんじゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,来るって　何が？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほら　音がする
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,来た来た
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.53,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほら　雪解け水が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:47.25,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,来るって雪解け水のことか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:50.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,すごい量だね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:54.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,数日前からかなり暖かかったからね　溜まってたはずだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:58.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんで一度にたくさん出てくるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:02.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大昔の都市の排水機能が残ってるせいだとかなんとか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:07.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,とにかく　大切なのは飲み水の確保
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:09.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,徒歩で行くの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:12.03,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そいつが降りられないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:13.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,靴を脱がなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:49.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,つめたっ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:52.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,つめたー
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.73,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,全部真っ青だね　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.65,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,空にいるみたいだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.68,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,足元気をつけろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,尖ったものが流れてきてるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:08.17,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,上を向いて歩こうよ　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:09.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,上をさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:12.27,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,足元に気をつけろって言ってんだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:16.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もったいないなー　こんなに空が青いのに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.81,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんなに空が青いし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:25.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,今日は洗濯日和だな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:33.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,寒っ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:35.93,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この紐は何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:40.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,流されたら危ないだろ　深い所もあるし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヘルメット取ったら？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:45.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,転んだら危ないだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:48.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,半裸ヘルメット
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:55.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やっぱり結構汚れてるなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,空ってなんで青いんだろうねー
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:02.51,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　ユー　なんでまったりしてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,水なら汲んだが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.01,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前も服を洗うんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.11,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,マジか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:18.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　ちーちゃん　空ってなんで青いの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:22.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔の人は海の青が映っているからなんて言ってたり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:23.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:28.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この水溜りよりもずーっと広く深く　水がある場所だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:32.91,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちの足元のずーっと下にまだあるとかないとか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:37.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔の人は海のそばで暮らしてたらしいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,見て見て　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:40.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だから聞けよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,バカ　急に走るな…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヘルメットかぶっててよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねえ　見て見て
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんでユーも濡れてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.11,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こけた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それより見て　これを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:12.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これは魚だな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:13.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.17,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,死んでるみたいだが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,魚って何なの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,水の中に住む生き物だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:24.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔は海とかにたくさんいたらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:29.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,人以外の生き物なんてもう生き残ってないと思ってたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よし　食べよう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えー　食べられるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:44.46,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔の人は食べてたらしいけど　大丈夫かな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:47.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,分解は始まってないみたいだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぁ　焼けば食べられるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:53.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,焼こう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,洗ったもの干してからね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:02.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねえ　水の中に住むってさ　どんな感じだろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:03.39,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:09.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,浮いたり沈んだり　ここの鰭をパタパタさせて進むらしいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:10.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,鰭…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.73,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんな感じで泳いでたのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そろそろ焼けたかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:22.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.39,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,熱いから気をつけろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:27.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:28.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あちっ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:38.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ど…どう？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:49.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うまい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:50.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんまり食べないでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:00.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,初めて食べる味だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,変な味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.69,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,次　次私
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,きれいになったね　服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:22.09,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こっちは肉が落ちてすっきりしたね　骨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,すっきりって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:27.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　どこから流れてきたんだろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:32.03,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やっぱり上層からじゃないかな　排水に混じって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:41.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,上の方へ行けば　いっぱいいるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いたらどうするの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:44.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:45.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べるか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:46.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:48.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.73,0:23:37.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さらば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:38.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,バイバーイ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.25,0:00:16.17,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我说 小尤
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.81,0:00:17.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这是哪里啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.99,0:00:24.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,谁知道 反正放眼望去一片白茫茫
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.46,0:00:28.46,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就好像这个世界只有我们俩一样
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.24,0:00:31.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,诗人真悠闲啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.35,0:00:36.25,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我可是瞪大着眼睛 在找能御寒的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.49,0:00:39.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还是说…
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.49,0:00:43.81,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,实际上我们已经死了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.04,0:00:46.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,正游荡在白茫茫的死后世界
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.80,0:00:49.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.91,0:00:52.23,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不吉利的话少说
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.12,0:00:58.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还有别捏雪球了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,为什么啊 我正捏得开心呢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.01,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,头好沉
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.37,0:01:05.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,而且好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.33,0:01:10.43,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 据说死后的世界很温暖哦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.06,0:01:14.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这么说的话 我们应该还活着吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.65,0:01:22.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.04,0:03:10.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,再…再不找个能过夜的地方就麻烦了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.20,0:03:10.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.38,0:03:28.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤 醒醒
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.17,0:03:31.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我没睡下去好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.33,0:03:40.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,楼…楼…楼房
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.68,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.57,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这这…这是什么设施啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,谁…谁知道呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,找…找个地方进去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,看…看不懂
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这里看起来很旧了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也不知道入口在哪
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.09,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,喂 快看 快看
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.72,0:04:39.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那…那个管道上完全没有积雪
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.93,0:04:44.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,融化了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是热的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我来开一枪看看
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是…是热水
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,热水
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.75,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还能怎么办 当然是…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,幸好有个状况不错的管道
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.30,0:06:24.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,浴缸完成了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,进去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.72,0:06:45.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这澡泡着好舒服 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.25,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好像已经很久没泡过澡了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.69,0:07:18.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,自从离开爷爷那之后 大概泡过两次吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.86,0:07:19.94,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是三次
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是吗 那这是第四次了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,复活了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,简直极乐世界
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.37,0:07:39.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,问你 极乐世界是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,指的是死后的世界吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好不容易复活了 太不吉利了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.81,0:07:48.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.17,0:08:02.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 泡得头晕了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好大的暴风雪
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.76,0:08:25.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.53,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,幸好找到了过夜的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.81,0:08:30.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.84,0:08:35.82,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们进入房屋后 用雪封住了入口
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.53,0:08:40.74,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,幸运的是 这里有一些能用来生火的有机废材
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.38,0:08:44.43,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 加点燃料进去
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.30,0:08:45.94,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.74,0:08:47.81,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,「好」说一次就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.68,0:08:49.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.13,0:08:56.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千真幸福啊 能把杂事全推给我一个人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.81,0:08:59.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,脑子不好使的家伙就只能干点体力活不是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你又不会读书写字
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.65,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你在写什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.14,0:09:12.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,可以说是我们旅行的日记 也可以说是日志
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,之前不就跟你说过了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.90,0:09:15.53,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.37,0:09:20.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我会写这记录 可也是为了你啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,记忆会变模糊 所以要记录下来
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,人活着 并不需要记忆
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.66,0:09:37.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,至少要记得吃没吃过饭吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,说来 今天我们吃过饭了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.62,0:09:42.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,吃过了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.39,0:09:46.94,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,书可是个好东西
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.37,0:09:51.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,自从古人在几千年前发明了书
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,人类一直在书上做记录
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.37,0:10:00.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们能知道以前的事 也是多亏了书
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.29,0:10:04.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千你一直很喜欢读书啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.21,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,读了爷爷好多书
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,然而大部分都烧了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.72,0:10:14.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,要说现在还带着的书 除开几本日记…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.98,0:10:17.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,一 二 三
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.88,0:10:18.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,一共四本啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.63,0:10:22.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.14,0:10:26.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.23,0:10:36.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也不知道世界上还剩多少书了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.18,0:10:38.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.14,0:10:43.73,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,火变小了 加点燃料进去
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.28,0:10:44.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.72,0:10:48.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,能烧的东西也没剩多少了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 已经没有废材了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.51,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,书…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.27,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,快灭火
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好烫 好烫
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.55,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,《河童》被…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.76,0:11:18.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,河童？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.18,0:11:22.27,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我刚说了书很宝贵的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,对不起 我没太注意听
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你倒是听啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.74,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,都说了对不起了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.41,0:11:36.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,混蛋 傻瓜 垃圾
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.92,0:11:38.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.64,0:11:39.55,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,别给我说「是」
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.09,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,算了 我睡了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.66,0:11:56.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.94,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,喂 小尤 快点
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 你还在生气吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.99,0:13:01.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.95,0:13:03.23,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,肯定在生气
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.69,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.54,0:13:24.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,哇 放晴了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.83,0:13:25.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,雪积起来了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么样 能发动起来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.82,0:13:32.77,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,勉强能
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.68,0:13:43.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我说 你还在生气吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.32,0:13:48.93,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,快上车
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.26,0:13:58.09,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就算书烧了 我们还有日记
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.51,0:14:08.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,只要坚持写下去 日记就会变成书
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.69,0:14:11.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤 你是不是瞎涂了什么东西
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.92,0:14:17.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.68,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,别瞎涂啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你的脸
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.69,0:14:27.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我才不长这样
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你睡觉的时候就是这样子
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.90,0:14:56.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好想再涂点东西啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.25,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,纸张很宝贵的 不行
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.74,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还有 你的字也写错了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.88,0:15:03.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.85,0:15:06.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我戳了？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.99,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就这里吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.85,0:15:16.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好大的太阳啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.73,0:15:19.93,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这段时间一直是这种天气
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.74,0:15:23.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所以应该快来了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,什么东西快来了？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,听 有声音
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.53,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,看 雪融水
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.82,0:15:47.25,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,原来是说雪融水快来了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.51,0:15:50.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好多啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.35,0:15:54.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,因为这几天都比较暖和 应该积攒了很多
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.49,0:15:58.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,为什么会突然涌出这么多啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.76,0:16:02.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,应该是很早以前的城市排水系统还在工作的关系吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.53,0:16:07.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,总之 我们得趁着这机会弄点饮用水
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.38,0:16:09.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,走过去吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.04,0:16:12.03,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这家伙下不去啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.23,0:16:13.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,得脱了鞋
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.85,0:16:49.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.81,0:16:52.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.73,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好蓝啊 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.65,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,感觉像在天上走
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.68,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,注意脚下
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,水流或许会把尖锐的东西冲过来
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.94,0:17:08.17,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,让我们抬着头向前走吧 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.66,0:17:09.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,抬起头来
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.87,0:17:12.27,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不是说了让你注意脚下吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.08,0:17:16.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,太浪费了 天空这么蓝
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.81,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,天这么蓝
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.86,0:17:25.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,今天适合洗衣服
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.26,0:17:33.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.85,0:17:35.93,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这绳子是干什么的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.56,0:17:40.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,被冲走的话多危险啊 而且有些地方水很深
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不把头盔摘了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.49,0:17:45.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,摔跤了也很危险
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.34,0:17:48.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,半裸头盔
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.84,0:17:55.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,果然好脏
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,天空为什么是蓝色的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.72,0:18:02.51,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我说小尤 别一个人在那优哉游哉的好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,水已经灌好了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.01,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你也来洗衣服
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.11,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.93,0:18:18.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我说小千 天空为什么是蓝色的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.16,0:18:22.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,以前的人说是因为天空反射了大海的颜色
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.98,0:18:23.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,大海？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.66,0:18:28.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那是个满是水的地方 比这个水潭还大得多 深得多
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.92,0:18:32.91,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有可能就在我们脚底下很深很深的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.79,0:18:37.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,据说老早以前 有些人就生活在海边
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,快看快看 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.48,0:18:40.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你倒是听我说话啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 别突然跑起来
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还好戴着头盔
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,快看快看
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你怎么也全身湿透了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.11,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,摔了一跤
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,快看这个
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.24,0:19:12.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这是鱼吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.05,0:19:13.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,鱼？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.17,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,看起来像是死了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,鱼是什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,生活在水里的生物
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.81,0:19:24.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,据说以前海里有很多
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.14,0:19:29.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我还以为现在这世界就只有人类了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好 吃了它吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这能吃吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.44,0:19:44.46,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,以前的人倒是吃它 但吃起来真的安全吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.90,0:19:47.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,虽说好像还没开始腐烂
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,算了 烤一烤应该能吃吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.96,0:19:53.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,烤吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,先把洗好的衣服晾好
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.21,0:20:02.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你说 生活在水里是什么感觉啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.92,0:20:03.39,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.87,0:20:09.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,应该是一会上浮一会下沉 然后拍着这里的鳍不断向前进吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.12,0:20:10.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,鳍…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.73,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,游起来的时候会不会就像那样呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,烤得差不多了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.78,0:20:22.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,开吃
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.39,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小心点 很烫
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.21,0:20:27.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.21,0:20:28.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.52,0:20:38.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.78,0:20:49.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.11,0:20:50.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我也来尝尝
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,别吃太多
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.83,0:21:00.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,第一次吃到这种味道
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有点怪
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.69,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,该我了 该我了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,衣服变干净了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.40,0:21:22.09,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这边是肉都没了 变成了干净的骨头
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,干净…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.17,0:21:27.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过 这家伙到底是从哪里冲过来的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.55,0:21:32.03,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,应该是混在排水管里 从上面冲下来的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.82,0:21:41.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,到上面去的话 会不会有很多鱼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有的话呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.82,0:21:44.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,吃掉
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.86,0:21:45.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,吃掉吗
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.24,0:21:46.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.36,0:21:48.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好主意
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.73,0:23:37.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,永别了
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.06,0:23:38.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,拜拜
